Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan's political honeymoon
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w54t
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Nov 1980
President-elect Reagan turns his honeymoon period into a Washington courtship ritual. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less